4. Concurrency

What:
  Number of Lambda instances
  running at same time

Types:
  Reserved    → guarantee X for one function
  Provisioned → pre-warmed, no cold start

Default limit:
  1000 per region
  Can request increase from AWS

Throttle:
  Limit exceeded → Lambda throttled
  Fix → SQS queue in front of Lambda

5. VPC Lambda

When to use:
  Lambda needs RDS access ✅
  Lambda needs private resources ✅

How:
  Configure VPC + private subnet + SG
  Lambda gets private IP

Problem:
  Cold start increases (ENI creation)
  Needs NAT Gateway for internet access

Best practice:
  Only put Lambda in VPC when necessary
  Not needed for S3, DynamoDB (use VPC endpoints)
